Alba later starred in Honey (2003), Sin City (2005), Fantastic Four (2005), Into the Blue (2005), Good Luck Chuck (2007) and Valentine‚Äôs Day (2010), establishing herself as a leading lady in both action and comedy films.

item.title: Katy Perry Knew the 'Truth' About Russell Brand Before Assault Claims
item.description: Katy Perry‚Äôs comments about ex-husband Russell Brand resurfaced after he was accused of sexual assault by multiple women. Perry, 38, described Brand, 48, as ‚Äúvery controlling‚Äù in a 2013 interview with Vogue ‚Äî and admitted she didn‚Äôt want to publicly share everything that led to their 2011 split. ‚ÄúAt first when I met him he wanted an equal, and I think a lot of times strong men do want an equal, but then they get that equal and they‚Äôre like, I can‚Äôt handle the equalness,‚Äù she said at the time.

item.description: Moneybagg Yo was served lawsuit papers during a recent event. A video obtained by The Neighborhood Talk shows the Memphis rapper signing bottles of his Del Dia Tequila brand. However, things turned awkward when a woman pretending to be a fan arrived with papers. ‚ÄúThank you,‚Äù she said before handing the rapper the legal docs. ‚ÄúYou‚Äôve been served.‚Äù Money appeared confused as he looked up to the camera and responded, ‚ÄúHuh?‚Äù ‚ÄúHave a good one,‚Äù the unnamed woman responded, walking away.
